  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Developing Pricing Logic**\n\nI\'m now focusing on `/src/components/PricingMatrix.tsx` to build the custom quote and booking functionality. The pricing matrix will include columns for \"Meio Turno (4h)\" and \"Turno Completo,\" as observed from the initial design (\"METODO PAME - Pricing\"). My immediate priority is to understand how these factors will influence the pricing logic and real-time calculation.\n\n\n**Refining Pricing Structure**\n\nI\'m now integrating the detailed pricing tiers for \"Meio Turno\" and \"Turno Completo,\" incorporating session types and monthly package discounts. I need to make these calculations in real-time. I\'m also planning to build a dynamic summary box displaying user-specific details from the triage form, offering a tailored estimate. Plus, I want to add deluxe add-ons with their specific prices, and have the box update prices in real time.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will now create the `/src/components/PricingMatrix.tsx` component. It replicates the luxurious, high-contrast bento-grid investment structure in Image 1. It renders Meio Turno (4h) vs Turno Completo (9h) with different columns, active selection states for \"Sess\303\243o Avulsa\" and \"Pacote Mensal\" options, and interactive checkboxes for the deluxe addons. I will add an interactive modal that confirms their custom-calculated scheduling based on the triage responses."
