  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Confirming Build Success**\n\nI\'m incredibly pleased to report a flawless first build, confirming successful compilation of standard React, TypeScript, Vite, and Tailwind v4. The next step involves double-checking if I need to declare any environment variables for this process.\n\n\n**Verifying Client-Side Compliance**\n\nI\'m now certain that no server-side components are necessary. The project perfectly aligns with the Single-View and No Secondary Architecture constraints. I\'ve confirmed that the client-side SPA setup, including styling, navigation, multi-step triage, and the Bento grid, requires no server setup or AI APIs, thus not requiring any keys. I\'ve also completed the final audit and updated `metadata.json`, and `index.html`, and created `src/types.ts` and `src/data.ts`.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have designed and implemented a fully responsive, pixel-perfect web application based on the \"Quiet Luxury\" **Silk & Stone** design system for **M\303\211TODO PAME**. \n\nHere is a summary of the achievements:\n\n*   **Identidade Visual \"Atmosfera PAME 2.0\"**: Configured high-contrast typography using the **Manrope** display font combined with **Material Symbols** and a selection of premium tones utilizing the brand\342\200\231s core purple (`#561668` & `#703081`) over warm off-white canvases.\n*   **Divided Split-Screen Entry (\"Welcome Screen\")**: Replicated the dual-action landing layout, separating **\"Para Resid\303\252ncias\"** (leads to triage) and **\"Para Especialistas\"** (leads to recruitment), wrapped around a central neumorphic badge using the high fidelity assets provided.\n*   **Client Triage Form (\"Triagem Invis\303\255vel\")**: Developed the 4-step interactive qualification funnel with progressive step trackers and custom counter overlays.\n*   **Bento-Grid Pricing Matrix**: Crafted the exact card architecture shown in the mockups, complete with interactive toggles for **\"Meio Turno (4h)\" vs. \"Turno Completo (9h)\"**, **\"Sess\303\243o Avulsa\" vs. \"Pacote Mensal\"**, and checkboxes for deluxe services (*Dobra T\303\251cnica, Passadoria de Autor, Polimento de Metais*).\n*   **Recruitment Candidacy Flow**: Implemented the specialist form with full validation and a simulated antecedents upload zone.\n*   **Smooth Animations & Flows**: Linked all pages in `src/App.tsx` using `motion` transitions for high-fidelity interactive state changes.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 2
      nanos: 727153786
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
